FuncDef: This command specifies the ingress or egress QoS profile to be used for the configuration of the ingress or egress QoS parameters of an MLFR bundle or a Frame Relay port with FRF.12 UNI/NNI fragmentation enabled. Note that qos-profile on ingress is only applicable to MLFR.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the profile number. The value can only be modified if the MLFR bundle or FR port is shut down. Values-1 to 128.
